[17/01/2019 12:32:41] <font color="#ffffff">(GRITAN)</font>
[17/01/2019 12:33:19] <font color="#ffffff">(Relinchos)</font>
[17/01/2019 12:33:21] <font color="#ffffff">(Gritos)</font>
[17/01/2019 12:33:23] <font color="#ffffff">¡Los mexicanos atacan!</font>
